{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb99d4615-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8","identifier":"/us/usc/t18/s3488"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3488"},"text":"§ 3488.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Intoxicating liquor in Indian country as evidence of unlawful introduction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The possession by a person of intoxicating liquors in Indian country where the introduction is prohibited by treaty or Federal statute shall be prima facie evidence of unlawful introduction.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb99d4616-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-25/ch645"},"text":"June 25, 1948, ch. 645","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/834"},"text":"62 Stat. 834","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb99d4617-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idb99d4618-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Historical and Revision Notes","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Based on ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s245"},"text":"section 245 of title 25","children":[],"tail":", U.S.C., 1940 ed., Indians ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1916-05-18/ch125/s1"},"text":"May 18, 1916, ch. 125, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/124"},"text":"39 Stat. 124","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The only change made was the insertion of the word “Indian” before “country”, to substitute specificity for generality. (See definition of “Indian country” in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s1151"},"text":"section 1151 of this title","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
